Title: An Act Changing the Name of Taal (Pulilan) Elementary School to Don Francisco Castro Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 854
An Act Changing the Name of Taal (Pulilan) Elementary School to Don Francisco Castro Elementary School
Section 1. The name of the Taal (Pulilan) Elementary School, situated at Barangay Taal, Pulilan, Bulacan, is hereby changed to Don Francisco Castro Elementary School.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 27, 1984
